<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP for PIN Change</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
        }
        .otp {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #ff5722;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Your OTP for PIN Change</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= name || "User" %>,</p>
        <p>Your OTP for changing your login PIN is:</p>
        <p class="otp"><%= otp %></p>
        <p>This OTP is valid for 10 minutes. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Thank you!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
